activity = single screen in an app

View = controls (Occam)

Intent is a messaging object you can use to request an action from another app component.
    (a) start an activity
    (b) start a service
    (c) deliver a broadcast

PendingIntent is simply a reference to a token maintained by the system describing the original data
used to retrieve it.simply a reference to a token maintained by the system describing the original
data used to retrieve it.